(57, 1, '2024-02-13 11:14:36', '2024-02-13 11:14:36', '<p>At Little Explorers, we offer a wide range of services designed to meet the unique needs of our young students and their families. Our services include:</p><ul><li>Stimulating and play-based educational programs for preschool-age children</li><li>Engaging activities to develop motor, cognitive, language, and social skills</li><li>Qualified and passionate teachers who create a positive and engaging learning environment</li></ul>		\n			<style>/*! elementor - v3.19.0 - 07-02-2024 */\n.elementor-widget-image{text-align:center}.elementor-widget-image a{display:inline-block}.elementor-widget-image a img[src$=\".svg\"]{width:48px}.elementor-widget-image img{vertical-align:middle;display:inline-block}</style>										<img width=\"416\" height=\"332\" src=\"http://localhost/PSWordpress/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unnamed.jpg\" alt=\"\" />													\n													<img width=\"275\" height=\"183\" src=\"http://localhost/PSWordpress/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/download-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" />													\n		<ul>\n<li>Collaboration with families to support the progress and development of each child</li>\n<li>Modern and secure facilities designed to inspire the curiosity and creativity of our students</li>\n</ul><br>We are committed to providing high-quality services that prepare children for academic success and life beyond preschool.<br><br> Contact us today to learn more about our services and how we can support your child on their learning and growth journey.', 'Services', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'services', '', '', '2024-02-13 15:21:56', '2024-02-13 15:21:56', '', 0, 'http://localhost/PSWordpress/wordpress/?page_id=57', 0, 'page', '', 0);
